{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C3540 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C3540 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Compiler Error C3540","pos":[597,617]},{"content":"'type': sizeof cannot be applied to a type that contains 'auto'","pos":[618,681]},{"pos":[688,821],"content":"The <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>sizeof<ept id=\"p1\">](../../cpp/sizeof-operator.md)</ept> operator cannot be applied to the indicated type because it contains the <ph id=\"ph1\">`auto`</ph> specifier.","source":"The [sizeof](../../cpp/sizeof-operator.md) operator cannot be applied to the indicated type because it contains the `auto` specifier."},{"content":"Example","pos":[830,837]},{"content":"The following example yields C3540.","pos":[841,876]},{"content":"See Also","pos":[1052,1060]},{"content":"auto Keyword","pos":[1065,1077]},{"content":"/Zc:auto (Deduce Variable Type)","pos":[1111,1142]},{"content":"sizeof Operator","pos":[1204,1219]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C3540 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C3540\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C3540\"\nms.assetid: 3c0c959c-e3b7-40eb-b922-ccac44bd9d85\ncaps.latest.revision: 8\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C3540\n'type': sizeof cannot be applied to a type that contains 'auto'  \n  \n The [sizeof](../../cpp/sizeof-operator.md) operator cannot be applied to the indicated type because it contains the `auto` specifier.  \n  \n## Example  \n The following example yields C3540.  \n  \n```  \n// C3540.cpp  \n// Compile with /Zc:auto  \nint main() {  \n    auto x = 123;  \n    sizeof(x);    // OK  \n    sizeof(auto); // C3540  \n    return 0;  \n}  \n```  \n  \n## See Also  \n [auto Keyword](../../cpp/auto-keyword.md)   \n [/Zc:auto (Deduce Variable Type)](../../build/reference/zc-auto-deduce-variable-type.md)   \n [sizeof Operator](../../cpp/sizeof-operator.md)"}